      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound driver\u2019s car featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a precise 6-speed manual transmission. The powertrain delivers exceptional throttle response via its individual throttle bodies, while the factory limited-slip differential ensures optimal power delivery through the rear wheels. Critical preventative maintenance has been performed, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to address known chassis weak points. The suspension features refreshed bushings and dampers, maintaining the communicative handling and lateral grip expected of the M-division. While the exterior shows minor road-wear, the drivetrain is robust, with a recent valve adjustment and fluid analysis confirming peak operating health.",
