    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously cared-for 2017 Porsche 718 Cayman in Graphite Blue Metallic. This vehicle has been maintained with an open-checkbook philosophy, serving as a reliable and thrilling weekend companion. The exterior retains a deep, mirror-like shine, though a close inspection will reveal a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel\u2014typical of a car that has been enjoyed on the open road. Inside, the black leather cabin is exceptionally clean; the seat bolsters show only light softening, and the interior remains free of odors or pet hair. All systems, including the dual-zone climate control and Porsche Communication Management, function exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health. It has a full service history, with a recent oil service and brake fluid flush performed within the last 1,000 miles. The tires are premium Michelin Pilot Sports with plenty of life left. This is a solid, honest example of a modern driver's car, offering a perfect balance of performance and daily usability. Sold with two keys and all original manuals.",
